{"word":"G4856 - συμφωνέω - symphōnéō - soom-fo-neh'-o - Agree together","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμφωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">symphōnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-fo-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Agree together</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒருமனப்பட்டிரு. ஒத்துக்கொள், கூடசம்மதி, ஒத்திரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to sound together"},{"paragraph":"2. to agree together"},{"paragraph":"3. to agree with one in making a bargain, to make an agreement, to bargain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4859 - σύμφωνος - sýmphōnos - soom'-fo-nos/4859\">G4859</a>; to be <i>harmonious</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>accord</i> (<i>be suitable</i>, <i>concur</i>) or <i>stipulate</i> (by compact): - agree (together, with).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2019/2019\">G2019</a>, <a href=\"#/G4856/4856\">G4856</a>, <a href=\"#/G4857/4857\">G4857</a>, <a href=\"#/G4858/4858\">G4858</a>, <a href=\"#/G4859/4859\">G4859</a>, <a href=\"#/G5455/5455\">G5455</a>, <a href=\"#/G5456/5456\">G5456</a>"}]}